owl:Ontology.dc:description: The Friend of a Friend (FOAF) RDF vocabulary, described using W3C RDF Schema and the Web Ontology Language.
owl:Ontology.dc:title: Friend of a Friend (FOAF) vocabulary

owl:AnnotationProperty.rdfs:comment: Indicates the class of individuals that are a member of a Group
owl:AnnotationProperty.rdfs:label: membershipClass

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: Indicates an account held by this agent.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: account

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: Indicates a homepage of the service provide for this online account.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: account service homepage

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: A current project this person works on.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: current project

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: A depiction of some thing.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: depiction

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: A thing depicted in this representation.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: depicts

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: The underlying or 'focal' entity associated with some SKOS-described concept.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: focus

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: An organization funding a project or person.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: funded by

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: Indicates an account held by this agent.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: account

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: A homepage for some thing.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: homepage

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: An image that can be used to represent some thing (ie. those depictions which are particularly representative of something, eg. one's photo on a homepage).
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: image

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: A page about a topic of interest to this person.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: interest

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: A document that this thing is the primary topic of.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: is primary topic of

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: A logo representing some thing.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: logo

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: Something that was made by this agent.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: made

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: An agent that made this thing.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: maker

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: A personal mailbox, ie. an Internet mailbox associated with exactly one owner, the first owner of this mailbox. This is a 'static inverse functional property', in that there is (across time and change) at most one individual that ever has any particular value for foaf:mbox.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: personal mailbox

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: Indicates a member of a Group
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: member

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: An OpenID for an Agent.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: openid

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: A page or document about this thing.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: page

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: A project this person has previously worked on.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: past project

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: A phone, specified using fully qualified tel: URI scheme (refs: http://www.w3.org/Addressing/schemes.html#tel).
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: phone

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: The primary topic of some page or document.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: primary topic

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: A link to the publications of this person.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: publications

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: A homepage of a school attended by the person.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: schoolHomepage

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: A theme.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: theme

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: A derived thumbnail image.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: thumbnail

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: A tipjar document for this agent, describing means for payment and reward.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: tipjar

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: A topic of some page or document.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: topic

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: A thing of interest to this person.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: topic_interest

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: A weblog of some thing (whether person, group, company etc.).
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: weblog

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: A work info homepage of some person; a page about their work for some organization.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: work info homepage

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: A workplace homepage of some person; the homepage of an organization they work for.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: workplace homepage

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Indicates the name (identifier) associated with this online account.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: account name

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: The age in years of some agent.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: age

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: The birthday of this Agent, represented in mm-dd string form, eg. '12-31'.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: birthday

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: The family name of some person.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: familyName

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: The first name of a person.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: firstName

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: A textual geekcode for this person, see http://www.geekcode.com/geek.html
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: geekcode

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: The gender of this Agent (typically but not necessarily 'male' or 'female').
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: gender

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: The given name of some person.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: Given name

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: The last name of a person.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: lastName

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: A .plan comment, in the tradition of finger and '.plan' files.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: plan

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: A string expressing what the user is happy for the general public (normally) to know about their current activity.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: status

owl:Class.rdfs:comment: An agent (eg. person, group, software or physical artifact).
owl:Class.rdfs:label: Agent

owl:Class.rdfs:comment: A foaf:LabelProperty is any RDF property with texual values that serve as labels.
owl:Class.rdfs:label: Label Property

owl:Class.rdfs:comment: A project (a collective endeavour of some kind).
owl:Class.rdfs:label: Project
